# Directories Bazel must not try to load as packages (ADR-MCPS-048 / #220).
# The demo video's npm tree vendors third-party packages (e.g. mathjax-full)
# that ship their own non-Bazel `BUILD` files, which break `bazel test //...`
# package loading. These are local/untracked and not part of the build graph.
demo/video/mcps-intro/node_modules
sdk/typescript/node_modules
